com.twistral.toriamath.core.geometry.vectors

Class TVec3

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.twistral.toriamath.core.geometry.vectors.TVec3

  • public class TVec3
extends java.lang.Object
    A fast and mutable 3D vector/point class.
    All methods either return a numeric value or this vector for method chaining purposes.
    Also take a look at TVec2 class for a 2D vector/point.
